name: WARUNG MAYONG BALI PANORAMA
address: Jl. Mayong-Gunungsari, Bestala, Kec. Seririt, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81153, Indonesia
review 1: Good expérience here for the lunch. Sate mix was really good and a nice view. Highly recommend.
review 2:
Great view over the jungle mountains and Sawa's.
The spring rolls and vegetable tempura are really good.
review 3: Nice place and has a great ricefield view to enjoy our delicious lunch.it is really recommended place to have a meal during your day tour in the north part of Bali.
review 4: Nice view. Decent food. A bit pricy
review 5: Mahdi delightful restaurant owner. Great food plus great conversation. I’d definitely visit again!

name: Mayong Bali Homestay
address: PXVG+WGQ, Bestala, Seririt, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81153, Indonesia
review 1: Stayed here for the second time. We love it here. The room is very nice. Air con and fridge work good. Smart tv and bed comfy and big. Has a great outdoor shower. Definitely recommend staying here. The staff are all very helpful and lovely. The restaurant out the front also has delicious food!! Tried many off their menu.
